sequenceDiagram
participant U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant BE as Backend
participant DB as MongoDB
participant CRON as CronJob

U->>FE: Enter credentials
FE->>BE: POST /api/v1/auth/login
BE->>DB: Verify user + password
DB-->>BE: User record
BE-->>FE: JWT token + profile
FE->>BE: PUT /api/v1/nutrition/profile
BE->>DB: Upsert profile
DB-->>BE: Profile saved
BE-->>FE: Profile response
FE->>BE: POST /api/v1/nutrition/foods
BE->>DB: Create FoodLog
DB-->>BE: Log saved
BE-->>FE: FoodLog response
CRON->>BE: Daily schedule tick
BE->>DB: Create Notification if due
DB-->>BE: Notification saved
BE-->>FE: Notification available